BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:VlUTUeeAhP0rwC0UQIet1
SUMMARY:BOARD OF DIRECTORS MEETING
DTSTAMP:20260317T070138Z
DTSTART:20260320T143000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Chamber's Board of Directors meets monthly to review organi
	zational business\, financial reports\, and strategic initiatives. These m
	eetings provide an opportunity for the board to discuss ongoing programs\,
	 evaluate progress toward goals\, and make decisions that guide the Chambe
